name: Elemental Grace Doriado
desc: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned (from your hand) while there are 6 or more different Attributes among the monsters in the GYs. Gains 500 ATK and DEF for every different Attribute among the monsters in the GYs. When your opponent would Special Summon a monster(s) (Quick Effect): You can banish 3 monsters from your GY; negate the Special Summon, and if you do, destroy that monster.
